            <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl font-black leading-tight">
                Contemporary Art in the <span class="protest-red">Modern Political Landscape</span> and Its Influence
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl">
                This exhibition is a statement of intent, arguing that art is not a passive observer of history but an activator of change, a force against institutional corruption, and a powerful language of transformation.
            </p>
